cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving neural machine translation models using monolingual data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which includes papers on natural language processing and machine translation. The paper also proposes a novel approach to training the models, which involves joint learning and EM optimization, which could fall under categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses neural networks, which could also fall under categories such as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
